---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Developers — Testnet Portal"
  description="Boing Network testnet: developer community, dApp registration, and success-based dApp incentive pool."
>
  <article class="portal-page role-hub developers-hub">
    <nav class="portal-nav">
      <a href="/testnet">Portal</a>
      <a href="/testnet/developers" class="active">Developers</a>
      <a href="/testnet/users">Users</a>
      <a href="/testnet/operators">Operators</a>
      <span id="portal-auth" class="portal-auth"></span>
    </nav>

    <div id="wrong-role-banner" class="wrong-role-banner" style="display: none;"></div>

    <div class="hub-hero">
      <h1>Developers</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Build dApps on testnet, register for incentive tracking, and qualify for grants. At mainnet, a <strong>dedicated portion of the ecosystem pool</strong> rewards successful dApps (success-based, with a value cap per dApp).
      </p>
      <div class="hub-ctas" id="hub-ctas">
        <a href="/testnet/register/developer" class="btn btn-primary">Register as developer</a>
        <a href="/testnet/sign-in" class="btn btn-secondary">Sign in</a>
        <a href="#dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">Go to dashboard</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="section steps-section">
      <h2>Your journey</h2>
      <ol class="steps-list">
        <li><strong>Register</strong> — Add your account ID and optional GitHub/Discord on the <a href="/testnet/register/developer">developer registration</a> page.</li>
        <li><strong>Get testnet BOING</strong> — Use the <a href="/network/faucet">faucet</a> for gas and deployment.</li>
        <li><strong>Build & deploy</strong> — Follow the <a href="/developers/quickstart">quickstart</a> (CLI, SDK). Deploy a contract.</li>
        <li><strong>Register your dApp</strong> — Add your contract below (or use <code>boing_registerDappMetrics</code> at mainnet) to track it for incentives.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="section dashboard-section" id="dashboard">
      <h2>Your dashboard</h2>
      <p class="muted">Register with your testnet account to see your registered dApps here. On mainnet, use <code>boing_registerDappMetrics</code> and the chain indexer for live metrics.</p>
      <div class="dashboard-load" id="dashboard-load">
        <label for="me-account">Account ID to load dashboard</label>
        <input id="me-account" type="text" placeholder="0x..." maxlength="66" />
        <button type="button" id="me-load-btn">Load dashboard</button>
      </div>
      <div id="dashboard-placeholder" class="dashboard-placeholder">
        <p>Registered dApps and metrics will appear here once you register and add contracts.</p>
        <p><a href="/testnet/register/developer">Register as developer</a> · <a href="/developers/quickstart">Quickstart</a></p>
      </div>
      <div id="dashboard-loaded" class="dashboard-loaded" style="display: none;"></div>
      <div id="dapp-register" class="subsection">
        <h3>Register a dApp (testnet)</h3>
        <p>Add a contract address to track it for testnet incentives. Enter your account ID (owner) if you're not logged in. At mainnet, use the RPC method <code>boing_registerDappMetrics</code>.</p>
        <form id="dapp-form" class="compact-form">
          <input id="dapp-owner" type="text" placeholder="Your account ID (0x..., optional if session exists)" title="32-byte hex account ID" />
          <input id="dapp-contract" type="text" placeholder="Contract address (0x...)" required />
          <input id="dapp-name" type="text" placeholder="dApp name (optional)" />
          <button type="submit">Add dApp</button>
        </form>
        <p id="dapp-message" class="form-message"></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>dApp incentive pool</h2>
      <p>
        A portion of the <strong>Community & Grants</strong> allocation is reserved for <strong>successful dApps</strong>: rewards are based on usage (e.g. fees generated), with a <strong>per-dApp value cap</strong> per epoch. Testnet participation qualifies you for grants and for inclusion in this ecosystem at mainnet. See
        <a href="https://github.com/chiku524/boing.network/blob/main/docs/BOING-BLOCKCHAIN-DESIGN-PLAN.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BOING-BLOCKCHAIN-DESIGN-PLAN.md</a>
        and
        <a href="https://github.com/chiku524/boing.network/blob/main/docs/DEVELOPMENT-AND-ENHANCEMENTS.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">DEVELOPMENT-AND-ENHANCEMENTS.md</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/developers/quickstart">Quickstart</a> — CLI, SDK, local dev</li>
        <li><a href="/network/testnet">Join Testnet</a> — Bootnodes, faucet</li>
        <li><a href="/network/faucet">Faucet</a> — Get testnet BOING</li>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/chiku524/boing.network/blob/main/docs/RPC-API-SPEC.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RPC API</a> — <code>boing_registerDappMetrics</code></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<script is:inline src="/portal-session.js"></script>
<script>
  (function () {
    var expectedRole = 'developer';
    var session = window.BoingPortalSession && window.BoingPortalSession.getSession();
    var authEl = document.getElementById('portal-auth');
    var wrongBanner = document.getElementById('wrong-role-banner');
    var hubCtas = document.getElementById('hub-ctas');
    var dashboardLoad = document.getElementById('dashboard-load');
    var meInput = document.getElementById('me-account');
    var loadBtn = document.getElementById('me-load-btn');
    var placeholder = document.getElementById('dashboard-placeholder');
    var loaded = document.getElementById('dashboard-loaded');

    function renderAuth() {
      if (!authEl) return;
      if (!session) {
        authEl.innerHTML = '<a href="/testnet/sign-in" class="auth-link">Sign in</a>';
        return;
      }
      var short = window.BoingPortalSession ? window.BoingPortalSession.shortAccount(session.account_id_hex) : session.account_id_hex;
      var path = window.BoingPortalSession ? window.BoingPortalSession.roleAppPath(session.role) : '';
      var signOut = '<button type="button" id="portal-signout" class="auth-signout">Sign out</button>';
      if (session.role !== expectedRole) {
        authEl.innerHTML = 'Signed in as <span class="account-short">' + short + '</span> · <a href="' + path + '">My hub</a> · ' + signOut;
        if (wrongBanner) {
          wrongBanner.style.display = 'block';
          wrongBanner.innerHTML = 'You’re signed in as <strong>' + session.role + '</strong>. <a href="' + path + '">Go to your dashboard</a> or sign out below.';
        }
        if (hubCtas) hubCtas.style.display = 'flex';
        if (dashboardLoad) dashboardLoad.style.display = 'block';
      } else {
        authEl.innerHTML = 'Signed in as <span class="account-short">' + short + '</span> · ' + signOut;
        if (wrongBanner) wrongBanner.style.display = 'none';
        if (hubCtas) hubCtas.style.display = 'none';
        if (dashboardLoad) dashboardLoad.style.display = 'none';
      }
      var so = document.getElementById('portal-signout');
      if (so) so.addEventListener('click', function () {
        if (window.BoingPortalSession) window.BoingPortalSession.clearSession();
        window.location.href = '/testnet';
      });
    }

    function loadDashboard(hex) {
      if (!loadBtn || !placeholder || !loaded) return;
      loadBtn.textContent = 'Loading…';
      placeholder.style.display = 'none';
      loaded.style.display = 'block';
      fetch('/api/portal/me?account_id_hex=' + encodeURIComponent(hex))
        .then(function (res) { return res.json().catch(function () { return {}; }); })
        .then(function (data) {
          if (!data.ok) { loaded.innerHTML = '<p class="err">' + (data.message || 'Failed to load.') + '</p>'; return; }
          if (!data.registered) { loaded.innerHTML = '<p>Not registered. <a href="/testnet/register/developer">Register as developer</a>.</p>'; return; }
          if (data.role !== 'developer') { loaded.innerHTML = '<p>This account is registered as <strong>' + data.role + '</strong>. Use the correct dashboard.</p>'; return; }
          var dapps = data.dapps || [];
          var html = '<p><strong>Registered as developer.</strong>' + (data.github_username ? ' GitHub: ' + data.github_username : '') + '</p>';
          if (dapps.length === 0) html += '<p>No dApps registered yet. Add one below.</p>';
          else {
            html += '<p><strong>Your dApps (' + dapps.length + '):</strong></p><ul class="dapp-list">';
            dapps.forEach(function (d) { html += '<li><code>' + (d.contract_hex || '').slice(0, 18) + '…</code>' + (d.name ? ' — ' + d.name : '') + '</li>'; });
            html += '</ul>';
          }
          loaded.innerHTML = html;
        })
        .catch(function () { loaded.innerHTML = '<p class="err">Network error. Is the API deployed?</p>'; })
        .finally(function () { if (loadBtn) loadBtn.textContent = 'Load dashboard'; });
    }

    renderAuth();

    if (session && session.role === expectedRole && session.account_id_hex) {
      loadDashboard(session.account_id_hex);
      if (meInput) meInput.value = session.account_id_hex;
    } else if (meInput && loadBtn && placeholder && loaded) {
      try { if (localStorage.getItem('boing_portal_account')) meInput.value = localStorage.getItem('boing_portal_account'); } catch (_) {}
      loadBtn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        var hex = (meInput.value || '').trim();
        if (!hex.startsWith('0x')) hex = '0x' + hex;
        if (hex.length !== 66) {
          placeholder.style.display = 'none';
          loaded.innerHTML = '<p class="err">Enter a valid 32-byte hex account ID.</p>';
          loaded.style.display = 'block';
          return;
        }
        loadDashboard(hex);
      });
    }

    var form = document.getElementById('dapp-form');
    if (form) {
      form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        var contract = (document.getElementById('dapp-contract') && document.getElementById('dapp-contract').value || '').trim();
        var name = (document.getElementById('dapp-name') && document.getElementById('dapp-name').value || '').trim();
        var ownerHex = (document.getElementById('dapp-owner') && document.getElementById('dapp-owner').value || '').trim() || '';
        if (!ownerHex.startsWith('0x')) ownerHex = ownerHex ? '0x' + ownerHex : '';
        var msgEl = document.getElementById('dapp-message');
        if (!contract || contract.length < 20) {
          if (msgEl) msgEl.textContent = 'Enter a valid contract address (0x...).';
          return;
        }
        if (ownerHex && ownerHex.length !== 66) {
          if (msgEl) msgEl.textContent = 'Account ID must be 32 bytes (64 hex + 0x).';
          return;
        }
        var ownerToUse = ownerHex || (session && session.role === 'developer' ? session.account_id_hex : '');
        if (!ownerToUse && meInput) ownerToUse = (meInput.value || '').trim();
        if (!ownerToUse.startsWith('0x') && ownerToUse.length === 64) ownerToUse = '0x' + ownerToUse;
        fetch('/api/portal/dapps', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify({
            contract_hex: contract.startsWith('0x') ? contract : '0x' + contract,
            owner_account_hex: ownerToUse || undefined,
            name: name || undefined,
          }),
        })
          .then(function (res) { return res.json().catch(function () { return {}; }); })
          .then(function (data) {
            if (msgEl) msgEl.textContent = (data.ok ? 'dApp registered.' : (data.message || 'API not available; try again later.'));
            if (data.ok && loaded && (meInput || session)) {
              var h = ownerToUse || (session && session.account_id_hex) || (meInput && meInput.value);
              if (h && h.length === 66 && loadBtn) { if (meInput) meInput.value = h; loadDashboard(h); }
            }
          })
          .catch(function () { if (msgEl) msgEl.textContent = 'Network error. API may not be deployed yet.'; });
      });
    }
  })();
</script>

<style>
  .portal-page { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; }
  .portal-nav { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
  .portal-nav a { color: var(--text-secondary); font-weight: 500; }
  .portal-nav a:hover, .portal-nav a.active { color: var(--accent-teal); }
  .portal-auth { margin-left: auto; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .portal-auth .account-short { font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent-teal); }
  .portal-auth a { color: var(--accent-teal); }
  .auth-signout { background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-tertiary); cursor: pointer; font-size: inherit; padding: 0; }
  .auth-signout:hover { color: var(--accent-teal); }
  .wrong-role-banner { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.35); border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .wrong-role-banner a { color: var(--accent-teal); font-weight: 600; }
  .hub-hero { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .hub-hero .lead { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
  .hub-ctas { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-teal), var(--accent-cyan)); color: var(--bg-primary); }
  .btn-secondary { background: rgba(34,211,238,0.15); color: var(--accent-teal); border: 1px solid rgba(34,211,238,0.3); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(34,211,238,0.25); }
  .steps-section { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .steps-list { margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.25rem; padding-left: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }
  .steps-list li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .steps-list a { color: var(--accent-teal); }
  .lead { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .section { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .section h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .section h3 { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .muted { color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .dashboard-placeholder { background: rgba(30,41,59,0.35); border: 1px dashed rgba(34,211,238,0.3); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .dashboard-placeholder p { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .compact-form { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .compact-form input { padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 6px; background: var(--bg-tertiary); color: var(--text-primary); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .compact-form button { padding: 8px 14px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--accent-teal); color: var(--bg-primary); font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
  .form-message { margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .dashboard-load { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .dashboard-load label { display: block; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .dashboard-load input { margin-right: 0.5rem; padding: 8px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 6px; background: var(--bg-tertiary); color: var(--text-primary); font-family: var(--font-mono); width: 320px; max-width: 100%; }
  .dashboard-load button { padding: 8px 14px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--accent-teal); color: var(--bg-primary); font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
  .dashboard-loaded { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .dashboard-loaded .err { color: var(--error-color, #f87171); }
  .dashboard-loaded .dapp-list { margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .section ul { color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.2rem; }
  .section code { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; }
</style>
